{"type": "article", "id": 17321, "title": "monaco 家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-10T06:20:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021150426WwMakcxiepRymf3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦设计师 Adam Nathaniel Furman 从罗马的建筑里吸取灵感，做了这一系列的家具。桌子和柜台都使用了密集排列的竖条管，令人联想起建筑上的圆柱和窗户。而桌子上的抽屉柜也是一个有趣的前后推拉方式，很活泼，适合年轻人。此外，这些家具都有一个更加大胆的配色，白色的主体搭配红色或紫色，很新颖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144424hg7TOIuKLlPdqztZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"599\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73227384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144425BjWCGz8tnOdQ7S30.jpg\" width=\"575\" height=\"668\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.16173913\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144426RPmZVr1dquwaYLAB.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"517\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261444269mfPLWla1AnsGg0z.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"548\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144427xFW9eHKfzaBjMvRY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"574\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70171149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}